---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Projects"
	description="Selected software engineering and machine learning projects by Ken Chang."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-05-11')}
>
	<p>
		Selected projects from school, internship, and personal portfolio work.
	</p>

	<h2>Epay Digital Payment System</h2>
	<p>
		A group project built during my software engineering internship at E.SUN Bank. The system
		provided users with a digital payment platform and separated front-end and backend concerns.
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Role: software engineer intern</li>
		<li>Stack: Spring MVC, Bootstrap 4, jQuery</li>
		<li>Context: E.SUN Bank internship project</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Amadeus - Smarter Play, Simpler Day</h2>
	<p>
		A senior project that recognized user emotions from facial expressions and used the result to
		recommend music. The project combined mobile development, computer vision, and a lightweight
		Python backend.
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Stack: Android Java, Firebase, YOLOv3, Python, Flask</li>
		<li>Topics: facial expression recognition, CNN, music recommendation</li>
	</ul>

	<p>
		The original portfolio page also includes demo videos hosted on Google Drive. I keep those as
		external references for now instead of moving large media files into this Astro site.
	</p>
</Layout>
